Firestrike left the base.  "Firestrike to Switchblade: I am off for a 
raid.  Well make contact in one cycle."  He took a large stride as 
he folded down into his rhino mode, heading due south.  "Here I 
come Autobots. " Opening a comm-link to Nightstrike he 
proceeded. "Nightstrike.  What's your situation, I am requiring a 
hand in raiding the Autobot base. Copy"
